bsite=[[Deadline Hollywood]]|date=August 23, 2013}}</ref>\n* [[Alexis Bledel]] as Stacey<ref name=\"cast\"/>\n* [[Dustin Ybarra]] as Archie, Gavin's best friend\n* [[Ashlie Atkinson]] as Nessa, Stacey's best friend<ref name=\"cast\"/>\n* [[Michael Ian Black]] as Brian, Stacey's uncle<ref name=\"cast\"/>\n* [[Jane Kaczmarek]] as Pam, Gavin's mother\n* [[Kurt Fuller]] as Michael, Gavin's father\n* [[Kerri Kenney-Silver]] as Gwen, Stacey's mother\n* [[Aasif Mandvi]] as Dave Coaches, Nessa's ex and a security guard for the [[Dave Matthews Band]]<ref name=\"cast\"/>\n\n==Production and release==\nThe series was scheduled to premiere on [[Fox Broadcasting Company|Fox]] as a mid-season replacement in the [[2013\u201314 United States network television schedule|2013\u201314 season]].<ref name=\"premiere\">{{Cite web|url=http://www.thefutoncritic.com/news/2013/05/13/fox-announces-primetime-slate-for-2013-2014-season-254005/20130513fox01/|title=FOX Announces Primetime Slate for 2013-2014 Season|date=May 13, 2013|work=The Futon Critic|accessdate=August 24, 2013}}</ref> On May 8, 2013, Fox placed a thirteen-episode order for the [[Single-camera setup|single-camera]] comedy.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/fox-comedy-series-orders-chris-519678|title=Fox Comedy Series Orders: Chris Meloni Entry, 'Brooklyn Nine-Nine,' 'Enlisted,' 'Us & Them'|date=May 8, 2013|last=Rose|first=Lacey|last2=Goldberg|first2=Lesley|work=[[The Hollywood Reporter]]|accessdate=May 12, 2013}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.tvguide.com/News/Fox-Fall-2013-Comedy-Brooklyn-Enlisted-Jack-1065183.aspx|title=Fox Orders Brooklyn Nine-Nine, Enlisted, Us & Them and Surviving Jack|date=May 8, 2013|last=Abrams|first=Natalie|work=[[TV Guide]]|accessdate=May 12, 2013}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.deadline.com/2013/05/fox-picks-up-andy-samberg-chris-meloni-comedies-us-them-and-enlisted-almost-doubles-new-series-volume/|title=Fox Picks Up Andy Samberg & Chris Meloni Comedies, 'Us &